STATE
v.
Ryan Gabriel GARCELL. No. 465A06-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 13, 2016. Malcolm Ray Hunter, Jr., Durham, for Garcell, Ryan Gabriel. Elizabeth Hambourger Koch, for Garcell, Ryan Gabriel. Jess D. Mekeel, Assistant Attorney General, for State of NC. Ted Bell, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th of June 2015 by Defendant to Hold in Abeyance the Time in Which to File Petition for Writ of Certiorari:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 13th of April 2016."
